NOTICE AND CLAIM OF LIEN
1.
The Red Mountain Ranch Owners Association, an Arizona Corporation, being
a Homeowners' Association organized to own, operate, and manage the
commonly held facilities. The Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and
Restrictions, Recorder No. 85 286511 imposes an annual assessment on
individual parcels of property within said subdivision and creates a lien of
assessment; the assessment is both a lien against the real property and the
personal obligation of the recorded owner or purchaser of said property.
2.
That the recorded owner or purchaser of:
LOT 121, OF PARCEL 6 AT RED MOUNTAIN RANCH, ACCORDING TO THE
PLAT OF RECORD IN THE OFFICE OF THE COUNTY RECORDER OF
MARICOPA COUNTY, ARIZONA, RECORDED IN BOOK 346 OF MAPS, PAGE 26
AND AFFIDAVIT OF CORRECTIOIN RECORDED AS 91-602058, OF OFFICIAL
RECORDS.
is/are: James A McHenry
the delinquent amount of $495.93
3.
Said assessments due create a continuing lien on the above described real
estate and continues to accrue along with interest, late fees, collection costs
and additional charges as approved by the Board of Directors.
